### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@contentType = application/json

# =============================================================================
# AUTHENTICATION ENDPOINTS (Mapped to /api/auth)
# =============================================================================

### 1. Register a New Account
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "developer@example.com",
  "password": "SuperSecurePassword123",
  "name": "Testname",
  "tier": "BASIC"
}

### 2. Login (This will automatically attach the HttpOnly cookie to subsequent requests)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "developer@example.com",
  "password": "SuperSecurePassword123"
}


# =============================================================================
# LINKS ENDPOINTS (Mapped to /api/links)
# =============================================================================

### 3. Check System Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/links/health

### 4. Create a Shortened Link (Protected - Requires Login Cookie)
POST {{baseUrl}}/links/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "url": "https://www.github.com",
  "custom_alias": "mygit"
}

### 5. Get All Links Belonging to a User (Protected - Replace '123' with actual User ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/links/user/123

### 6. Redirect to Original URL (Public Link - See Router Note Below)
GET {{baseUrl}}/links/r/mygit

### 7. Delete an Existing Link (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/links/delete
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "link_id": "replace-with-actual-link-id"
}

# =============================================================================
# LOGOUT ENDPOINT
# =============================================================================

### 8. Logout (Clears the Auth Cookie Session)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout